des:
Come along with Willy, our friendly host, on a fantastic quest for knowledge. We have thousands of fun questions about History, Sports, Art, Entertainment, Geography and Science.
Challenge your friends and family or try to beat your high score. Think you’re on a roll? Try Challenge Mode!
Start playing now! Just say “Alexa, play Trivia Crack”.
